ch.ethz.inspire.emod.model

Class Revolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.ethz.inspire.emod.model.APhysicalComponent
      • ch.ethz.inspire.emod.model.Revolver

  • public class Revolver
extends APhysicalComponent
    General revolver model class. Implements the physical model of a revolver. From the input parameter tool position, the requested motor torque is calculated and speed Assumptions: Intertia forces are dominant. Simple bang-bang controller for position changes. Inputlist: 1: Tool : [1] : Number of the tool which shall be used Outputlist: 1: Torque : [Nm] : Calculated torque 2: RotSpeed : [rpm] : Requested rotational speed Config parameters: Inertia : [kgm3] : Revolver Interia NumberOfTools : [1] : Number of tool positions on the revolver MaxTorque : [Nm] : Maximum torque acting on the revolver
    Author:
    simon
